title: 158: Top RB draft prospects, talking to BYU RB Jamaal Williams
itunes:title: 158: Top RB draft prospects, talking to BYU RB Jamaal Williams
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks discuss the upcoming crop of running backs in the 2017 NFL Draft. DJ and Bucky break down the depth at the position with Christian McCaffrey, Leonard Fournette and some surprising names. BYU running back Jamaal Williams also joins the show to talk about how he's preparing for the NFL Draft.
